Values.AZURE_TENANT_ID: <ID of the tenant from app registration> in Azure AD
Values.AZURE_CLIENT_ID: <Application ID from client registration> in Azure AD
Values.AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET: <Client secret from client registration in Azure AD
Values.webproxy_url: <url from the creation a smee channel e.g http://smee.io/adasfsdf>
Values.ADOToken: <personal access token from azure dev ops>
Values.UserStoryName: <Name used in ADO to represent user story work items likely 'User Story'
Values.BugName: Name used in ADO to represent bug work items likely 'Bug'
Values.UserStoryDescriptionField: Field used as the description in the user story work item type.  It's likely System.Description
Values.BugDescriptionField: Field used as the desctiption in the bug work item item.  It's likely Microsoft.VSTS.TCM.ReproSteps
Values.DefaultIteration: Iteration to place work items into.  e.g Project\November
Values.GitClientSecret: Secret used when setting up the GitHub app
